                                    <br>
https://www.engineering.columbia.edu/news/ai-discovers-not-every-fingerprint-unique
                                        <br>
https://edition.cnn.com/2024/01/12/world/fingerprints-ai-based-study-scn/index.html                </div>
            ]]>
